OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1783779570
OL,3,CMan fined #40,000 for unlicensed tree
OL,4,Cfelling and habitat damage
OL,6,FRural Crime Team officer Police
OL,7,FConstable Nicholas Hodge said:
OL,8,F"Welch's disregard of environmental
OL,9,Fand wildlife laws, and his decision to
OL,10,Frepeatedly ignore expert advice has
OL,11,Fled to potentially irreparable damage
OL,12,Fto a protected species and their
OL,13,Fhabitat."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
